A,K
A' = A^{-1}=\bar{A}\mbox{ and } \bar{K} = AK\bar{A},
A'
\bar{A}
A^{-1}
K
K = \begin{bmatrix} i &  0 \\\ 0 & \overline{i}\end{bmatrix}
A = \begin{bmatrix} 0 & 1 \\\ 1 & 0\end{bmatrix}
A^{-1} = A = A' = \overline{A}
AK\overline{A} = AKA = \begin{bmatrix} \overline{i} & 0 \\\ 0 & i\end{bmatrix} = \overline{K}
